         <notesStmt>
            <note type="summary">1. Rovigo requests a copy of Benjamin ha-Kohen's Sefer
                            ha-Kawwanot. 2. He will append a list of the books in his possession to
                            the letter so that when Z.? travels to the Holy Land he will be able to
                            order copies of books that are missing in his collection. 3. Question
                            regarding Shulḥan ʿArukh and a certain minhag that concerns
                            prayer.</note>
            <note type="incipit" xml:lang="he">מי כחכם, ומי כיודע פשר</note>
